Invocation Name: rick roll
des: Who doesn't know what a RICK ROLL is? What would be better than having Alexa RICK ROLL someone. For the uninitiated, RICK ROLLING is a classic internet prank in which a specific, infectious hit from the 80's is switched to play over the intended song/video/etc; To say any more may give it away. Just say, "ALEXA, RICK ROLL" and watch the magic unfold.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
